title: [RG.REBOOT] The Conjuring (2013) CAM NEW AUDIO {REPACK}
description:
Movie Notes 
 	~~~~~~~~~~~
	Paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren work to help a family terrorized by a dark presence in their farmhouse.

	Rip Notes
	~~~~~~~~~
	Audio is a personal recording done with a Sony ICD-P620.

	Video is from: http://kickass.to/the-conjuring-2013-hdcam-new-source-x264-mp3-crewsade-t7677358.html

	Audio was recorded before any cams had been released, but I did not have the proper
	OS to copy the audio over.

	I'm sorry about the person next to me coughing and the people behind me talking.
	I partially gave up editing this, as I was busy with other things.

	Audio ran though a few filters to try to remove crackling and that hazy 'zzzz' sound.

	Enjoy!
